    "title": "Air India Digital Technologies is Hiring: Guest Relations Manager (Lead)",
    "description": "Air India Digital Technologies invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Guest Relations Manager at our Hyderabad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Air India Digital Technologies:\nAir India Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Hyderabad, Telangana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Air India Digital Technologies!",
